GeneratedClassName

The name to use for the generated injector class.

Declaration
public string? GeneratedClassName { get; set; }
Property Value
Type Description
string
Remarks

This value may be null if no custom class name is specified. If no custom name is specified a default value of "GeneratedXyz" will be used, where Xyz is the annotated interface's name with the leading "I" removed, if there is one.
